name: Sewer
description: After anhilating Korax, you wonder what they meant about other, greater players... Suddenly, out of nowhere, your most trusted advisor snatches the chaos orb from your grasp and takes off. You pursue the traitor and manage to knock the orb from his hands... And into a sewer!!!! You both rush in after it. It is now truly a fight to the Death, you now know what they meant about other players, for two more have joined the hunt. Your once great allies have become your worst enemies in a no holds barred, brawl for domination of the universe! All inside a SEWER! Now, what more could you ask for?
